we are now able to save *.mogul files for each package

what needs to be done:
- also save section files
- also save author files
- cause --publish to create a pkg, install doc, and update db

A makefile can now also contain contact info in the form of
a single record or a list of such records. A makefile with
contact info need not contribute anything else.

makefile(
  contact :
    o(
       mogul : 'mogul:/duchier/denys'
       name  : 'Denys Duchier'
       email : 'duchier@ps.uni-sb.de'
       www   : 'http://www.ps.uni-sb.de/~duchier/'))

ozmake --mogul=put              (DONE!)
ozmake --mogul=put -p PKG
ozmake --mogul=del -p MOG
ozmake --mogul=del -p PKG
ozmake --mogul=print
ozmake --mogul=print -p PKG
ozmake --mogul=db               (DONE!)
ozmake --mogul=db -p MOG
ozmake --mogul=db -p PKG
ozmake --mogul=fix

